column1: Student Discipline Data by Race and Gender

*To provide meaningful results and to protect the privacy of individual students, data are displayed only when the total number of students in a group is at least 10 and when the performance of individuals would not be disclosed. Data for groups less than 10 are displayed with an asterisk (*).
Note:  Totals are unduplicated and students are counted only once for each type of action.
